# üîç Wireshark: Network Traffic Analysis

## Objective
Capture and analyze insecure network traffic to detect sensitive information leaks.

## Activities
- Captured HTTP traffic containing login credentials.
- Applied filters: `http`, `ftp`, `tcp.port==80`.
- Located usernames and passwords transmitted in plain text.

## Key Tools
- Wireshark
- Kali Linux VM

## Lessons Learned
- Importance of encryption (HTTPS/TLS).
- How attackers can sniff unprotected network communications.
